      <title>오늘 서울 체감 영하 7도… 곳곳에 눈·비도</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/03/17/PYENW7DTSJH35FAKAN4KKEVXH4/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/03/17/PYENW7DTSJH35FAKAN4KKEVXH4/</guid>
